prompt: Given the video of the red sports car with a shattered windshield and severe damage in the garage, instantly replace all crash damage with artistic elements: the crumpled metal becomes polished steel sculptures, the torn airbags and interior damage become transparent glass wings, and the shattered windshield is now a colorful stained glass panel emitting radiant light.

Given the video of the person holding a glowing crystalline flower with sparkling particles next to a glass mister bottle containing shimmering liquid, transform the flower instantly back into a natural red rose planted in the sand, and restore the mister bottle's liquid to clear water.

Given the video of the nighttime city skyline with illuminated buildings and green trees, transform the buildings into futuristic galactic observatories with large telescopic domes and cosmic light displays. The trees below become glowing bioluminescent flora, and the dark blue sky transforms into a vivid star field with distant galaxies and nebulae.

Given the video of the chef transformed into a glowing open recipe book with animated pages in the kitchen, transform the book back into the chef wearing the orange, black, and white argyle jacket, restoring the original human form and removing the glowing text and illustrations, with the kitchen background unchanged.

Given the video of the frying pan cooking a bubbly omelet batter with diced red bell peppers and a black spatula inside, instantly transform the pan’s contents into rich soil with small green plants and red flowers blooming upright. Change the spatula into a small garden trowel resting on the pan’s edge, maintaining the warm natural kitchen lighting.

Given the video of the mythological tableau with the goddess, glowing infant, celestial messenger, stone altar, floating flames, and ethereal foliage, transform the woman back into a regular mother wearing a burgundy sweater holding a baby in yellow. Revert the child to a young blond child in casual clothes. Change the stone altar back into a wooden dining table with plates, utensils, lit candles in glass holders, and fresh tomatoes under warm indoor lighting.

Given the video of the tropical resort pool area at night with glowing bioluminescent water, illuminated building and palm trees, and flickering fireflies, transform the scene instantly back to daytime with natural daylight, clear blue pool water, and the white pyramid-roofed building surrounded by palm trees.

Given the video of two digital avatars in cyberpunk suits at a holographic news desk with a holographic U.S. Capitol behind them, transform both avatars back into male news anchors wearing formal suits and ties. Replace the holographic news desk with a modern physical desk, and change the lower third text back to standard broadcast font with the original headline and subheading.

Given the video of the gray and white cat with a real bird perched on the laptop keyboard and the screen off, transform the scene so the bird disappears and the laptop screen displays the video of the small bird perched on the wire against a blue sky.

Given the video of the man dressed as a futuristic time traveler standing in front of a hovering vehicle with glowing blue lights and a shimmering portal background, transform the vehicle back into a standard white pickup truck with a ladder rack. Change the man's clothing back to a striped button-up shirt with rolled-up sleeves and restore the forest background.

Given the video of the futuristic robot command center hallway, transform the mechanical airlock door back into a simple white fire exit door with an EXIT sign above it. Change the high-tech glass interface door back into a plain white door with a standard round doorknob. Alter the mechanized elevator portal back into a normal elevator door labeled '3'. Replace the metallic floor with wooden flooring and return the lighting to warm, neutral tones, restoring the quiet hallway.

Given the video of the young woman’s profile with braid transformed into living vines and flowers, transform the vines back into thick, neatly braided hair with natural texture and shine, restoring the original outdoor background.

Given the video of the person on a traditional subway platform with rusted metal pillars and blurred trains, transform the entire scene into a glowing cyberspace platform with neon digital structures replacing the physical subway. The person's clothing gains digital patterns, the stylus emits holographic light, and floating 3D data streams surround them, replacing all subway elements.

Given the video of the futuristic bioluminescent urban oasis at night, transform the scene back to a bright modern sunny sidewalk café with natural palm trees, a neutral pergola, and ordinary pavement. The people revert to casual everyday clothing, the interviewer holds a standard microphone, and all glowing bioluminescent creatures and lighting effects vanish, restoring natural daylight and shadows.

Given the video of the mossy tree stump surrounded by pine needles with a person’s feet nearby in a pine forest, transform the stump instantly into an ancient, ornately carved wooden chest embedded in the forest floor. The chest is partially open, emitting glowing golden light and revealing mysterious artifacts inside, with pine needles pushed aside around it. The person’s feet remain standing beside the chest.

Given the video of the young man wearing a collar emitting colorful musical notes and sound waves with subtle rhythmic movement against a vibrant swirling background, transform the scene back to the young man calmly fastening a plain black collar while seated on a dark couch with a neutral grey wall background. Remove the musical notes, sound waves, and colorful background.

Given the video of the news anchor with a swirling, glowing time portal backdrop, transform the portal back into the original city skyline. Restore the studio lighting to its original steady state, keeping the anchor's suit and bow tie unchanged.

Given the video of the otter biting a glowing molten lava rock outdoors, transform the lava rock instantly back into a large translucent red ice block resembling frozen fruit juice. The otter's fur returns to its natural wet appearance, and the environment remains unchanged.

Given the video of two young adults enjoying a casual picnic on patterned blankets in a natural field during late afternoon, transform the scene instantly into a lively Renaissance marketplace. Replace their casual modern clothing with period-accurate Renaissance attire, transform the picnic table into a wooden market stall displaying bread, cheeses, fruits, and olives for sale, convert the surrounding wildflowers into bustling market stalls with villagers in historical costumes, and change the vintage guitar into a lute on a wooden bench.

Given the video of the desert resort above a subterranean crystal cavern, transform the scene back so the resort is on solid desert ground with opaque floors and walls, removing all visible crystals and underground waterfalls beneath the surface.

Given the aerial video of the tranquil mountain road with cars traveling through snow-dusted fields and rustic houses, instantly transform the entire road into a glowing transparent magnetic levitation transit tube with pods replacing cars, change houses into futuristic eco-domes, and convert snow patches into shimmering holographic projections over the fields.

Given the video of the woman as an ethereal autumn spirit with flowing leaf-like hair and a cloak of autumn leaves, transform her instantly back into a woman wearing a deep red blouse standing in the sunlit garden with natural hair waves, normal background lighting, and no floating leaf particles.

Given the video of the man silently observing static abstract paintings in the wooden hallway, transform the paintings so they become animated, rippling underwater scenes projecting three-dimensional glowing aquatic lifeforms such as jellyfish and fish into the hallway. The lighting changes from warm to a cool underwater ambiance.

Given the video of the bustling pedestrian street café scene in photorealistic style, transform the entire video so that all elements—the café chairs, umbrellas, people, buildings, street lamps, and plants—are now rendered as dynamic impressionist oil painting brushstrokes in vivid colors, creating a living impressionist artwork.

Given the video of the fully carved pumpkin with glowing eyes and smoke, transform the scene so the pumpkin is shown mid-carving by a hand with a black knife, without any glowing light or smoke present.

Given the underwater video showing the man on the sandy seabed with coral reefs and tropical fish, instantly transform the scene back to the man standing knee-deep in shallow ocean water with the beach, bright sky, and forested island clearly visible on the horizon above the water.

Given the video of the modern Toyota car interior with a physical dashboard and infotainment screen, transform the entire dashboard and steering wheel area into floating transparent holographic displays. Replace all physical buttons and screens with vibrant 3D interactive holograms, while maintaining the same parking lot view outside.

Given the video of the 6.2-liter V8 engine with mechanical parts, transform all engine components into a futuristic miniature cityscape with skyscrapers, bridges, and roads. Add glowing windows, neon lights, flying vehicles moving between structures, and animated digital billboards.

Given the video of the middle-aged man on the American football sideline dressed in a white blazer and t-shirt, instantly transform his attire into a glowing white tactical suit with blue energy lines. Replace the stadium background with a sleek sci-fi command center filled with digital maps and star charts, projecting holographic interfaces around his hands, and position him as a futuristic time-traveling commander.

Given the video of the cascading veil of translucent, radiant light flowing into the pool, transform it instantly back into a dense, textured waterfall of real water crashing down with droplets and mist, removing all light effects and luminescence.

Given the animated video of miniature robot pedestrians crossing a cartoon-style city street with hovercraft vehicles, instantly transform the robots back into realistic human pedestrians wearing winter jackets and backpacks. Change the cartoon buildings back to realistic storefronts like Ann Taylor and ALDO, replace hovercrafts with yellow taxis, and restore natural city sounds.

Given the video of journalists and photographers in modern outdoor gear with cameras and tripods in a clear daylight mountain field, transform all their clothing into detailed steampunk time traveler costumes with brass goggles and leather gear. Replace their cameras and tripods with glowing, mechanical temporal devices. Change the sky to a surreal twilight with auroras and scatter futuristic artifacts on the grassy terrain.

Given the video of the enchanted forest with glowing bioluminescent trees and flickering lights, instantly transform all trees back into snow-covered village houses tightly packed on the hillside, preserving the snow-capped mountains and pale blue sky.

Given the video of the mythical guardian in ornate armor holding a glowing orb on an ancient coliseum floor, transform his appearance back into the young football player wearing the blue and red FC Barcelona jersey preparing to kick a football on the stadium pitch, removing the glowing orb, magical runes, and ethereal light beams.

Given the video of the time-warped park scene with frozen racers and translucent movement echoes, instantly restore all figures to normal motion in a sack race and remove all temporal echoes and dreamlike environmental effects, returning to a lively sunny park with joyful participants.

Given the aerial video of the sunken ancient city underwater with stone ruins and tropical fish, transform the scene back into a tropical island pier with rustic wooden huts above clear shallow turquoise water, revealing coral patches and sandy seabed, with the small traditional boat floating near the pier.

Given the video of the floating village on islands suspended in the sky with glowing villagers, transform the village back to a grounded mountain settlement with stone and mud houses and villagers in traditional clothing. The floating islands merge back into the earth, and the starry sky with auroras is replaced by snow-covered mountain peaks and an overcast sky.

Given the video of the water surface as a mirror reflecting a cosmic sky, transform the surface instantly back to a natural, clear water surface with sunlight reflections and visible underwater textures, removing all celestial reflections.

Given the video of the futuristic flying cars hovering above the parking spots with neon trims and anti-gravity engines, instantly transform all the vehicles back into stationary, polished Porsche sports cars and high-end SUVs parked on the asphalt with reflective glass and shining rims.

Given the video of the black mesh wastebasket containing crumpled brown paper balls with one paper ball falling, transform the contents instantly so that all paper balls become vibrant green saplings and blooming flowers. The falling paper ball is replaced by a falling green leaf, and the saplings gently sway as if in a breeze.

Given the video of the black-gloved hand holding a marine radio with an antenna emitting colorful waves and pulsing red and white ropes on a white sailboat panel, transform the radio antenna back to a static upright position with no light or sound waves. Simultaneously, transform the red and white ropes back to taut, secured ropes, restoring the calm and silent atmosphere.

Given the video of the man in a wild explorer outfit standing next to a jungle branch with an exotic bird perched where the trench coat was, instantly transform the jungle branch back into a clothing rack with formal shirts, jackets, and a dark trench coat hanging on it. Change the exotic bird back into the dark trench coat, and revert the man’s outfit to a navy blue suit. Replace the dense green foliage and flowers with the plain white wall background.

Given the video of the child pointing at a white plate transformed into a miniature ecosystem with moss, flowers, insects, and a waterfall, transform the plate instantly back into an empty white plate with crumbs, removing all ecosystem elements while keeping the rest of the scene unchanged.

Given the video of the yellow Audi R8 as a living biomechanical creature with blinking eyes, breathing exoskeleton, and glowing bioluminescent Audi rings, transform it back into the photorealistic yellow Audi R8 sports car. Restore the static glowing red taillights, black honeycomb grille, and fixed Audi rings on the rear with a glossy finish.

Given the aerial video of the village floating above the lake as a magical island, transform the village back down onto the hillside land, restoring the terracotta rooftops and greenery to their original position on the ground, removing the floating effect and glowing lights.

Given the video of the plated dish with fireworks above the avocado, glowing lantern mango chunks, and shimmering embers sauce, transform the fireworks back into red chili flakes, the glowing lanterns back into mango chunks, and the shimmering embers back into brown sauce with sesame seeds.

Given the video of the dynamic news collage with swirling headline snippets and abstract silhouette, transform the background back into a solid dark blue backdrop with visible partial letters, restore the clear and static news ticker with the text 'WINFREY DEFENDS HARRY & MEGHAN AS SHE TALKS BABY GIFT', refocus the camera to a static view on the person speaking, returning to the formal televised interview setting.

Given the video of the elemental guardian clad in bark armor with molten lava ribbons for a sash, standing by a pond reflecting flickering flames and surrounded by crackling bamboo, transform the figure back into a person wearing an olive-green robe with a bright red fabric sash trailing behind. Restore the pond to a calm reflective state without firelight, remove floating embers, and silence the bamboo stalks to their natural peaceful condition.

Given the video of the quiet city intersection with a human street cleaner pushing a cart, transform the street cleaner and cart into a giant glowing jellyfish floating above the ground. Change the stone buildings to appear melted and bending like wax, alter the street lights to emit soft pastel colors, and replace the cars with floating orbs of light drifting slowly.

Given the video of the young man holding a futuristic time-travel device with glowing blue lights and holographic controls, transform the device instantly back into a standard professional DSLR camera with a large lens and rig, removing the blue aura and temporal distortions.
